---
alwaysApply: true
---

UI is implemented using Dioxus.

Rules:

- Components must not contain business logic.
- Components call application services.
- State should be minimal and UI focused.
- Avoid raw RSX when a Dioxus component already exists from: https://dioxuslabs.com/components
- All texts must be translatable using .flt files, which are in the i18n folder, so keys will be used to identify strings, including error strings.
